# (``(sk|pk|rk)_(test|live)_[0-9a-z]{10,99}``) because the suffix is 11
# chars. The test sets ``settings.stripe_secret_key`` to a non-empty
# truthy value to exercise the live-pricing branch of the page builder;
# nothing more. (Literal omitted here on purpose — gitleaks scans the
# ignore file too, and quoting the string would re-trip the same rule.)
